General.Name: OlympCoin
General.Description: OlympCoin is a X11 cryptocurrency dedicated to celebrate both summer and winter olympic games. Its distribution is based on POW and POS, but also on a Country winning distribution, which means that if your favourite country wins a medal you will get a prize too. The coin's infrastructure is built around the olympic games, rewards are 31 OLYMP/block as this years Summer Olympics is the XXXI. one, and from 2018 the reward will be reduced to 23 celebrating the XXIII Winter Olympic games.
